**Creating Virtual Machine and running Apache2 server application.**

1. Created Azure VM of Linux (ubuntu 20.04) with size Standard B1s.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

1. Make sure to keep port 22 and 80 open. Port 22 to make SSH connection with local host and port 80 ie http to allow the application to run on the browser.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

1. Login to linux server

![](data:image/png;base64,)

1. Install Apache2 on the Linux server.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

1. Checking in browser the access of apache2 server application by putting the public IP address of the server.
